# API base URLs are OPTIONAL. Leave them unset to use same-origin relative
# paths — the SPA is served behind a reverse proxy (nginx in the built image,
# Vite's dev proxy during `pnpm dev`) that routes /catalog and /user-progress
# to the backend services. Set these only to target absolute backend URLs,
# e.g. when running the SPA against remote services.
# VITE_USER_PROGRESS_URL=http://localhost:8081
# VITE_CATALOG_URL=http://localhost:8082
